Class EdgeSequence

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.mesakit.graph.collections.EdgeSequence
All Implemented Interfaces:
Bounded, Iterable<Edge>
Direct Known Subclasses:
WorldEdgeSequence
public class EdgeSequence extends Object implements Iterable<Edge>, Bounded
An arbitrary sequence of edges. Wraps Iterable and adds convenience methods for working with edge sequences.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
